如是說：<br />\n<br />\n「如市民提出要求，軍裝警務人員應出示委任證，除非：<br />\n(a) 情況不容許；或<br />\n(b) 出示委任證會影響警隊行動及／或危及有關人員的安全；或<br />\n(c) 要求不合理。」<br />\n<br />\n請問犯左邊條 所以唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據《警察通例》第 20-14(2) 條，便衣人員「不論是否當值，<span style=\"color: red;\">在與巿民接觸和行<span style=\"color: red;\">使警察權力時」，一概必須表明身分及出示委任證</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n定係呢樣唔係警察權力 普通市民都可以問人拎黎睇?"},{"pid":"ece229f65d896bbeb0e3e031c52f0a888419819d","tid":1373933,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe5979616901d2a799be8d2f77118467683910f","tid":1373933,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3SkKJNf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3SkKJNf.png&h=6e31367b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胸前個位 唔係用黎放委任證? 係唔係又係設計上無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通用黎放回鄉證?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9f0812a65308a4c2a0f689c6db32160ce5234b","tid":1373933,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"無人推 係唔係已經接受左係合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c0b7ae3540cb08b9e4161003de3ade239641f4","tid":1373933,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ef9127bf9d70410a3b501f9aaa0364757da3b6","tid":1373933,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.g